title: Football: ISU nabs commitment from Texas defensive back
text:
Iowa picked up a verbal commitment from Lake Ridge High School defensive back Arnold Azunna on Friday night. 
Azunna, a two-star Rivals.com prospect, announced his decision on Twitter. 
“After a Great Win I’m Extremely Blessed To Say I’m Committing to THE Iowa State University #GoCyclones,” Azunna tweeted. 
Azunna, who is 6-foot, 187 pounds, visited for the Kansas game last week. He is the 10th member of the 2016 class. Rules for posting comments
